high_descs: Turn left and walk toward the door, then hang a left and walk over to the white dresser.
Pick up the dirty black rag off of the dresser.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the counter.
Put the dirty black rag in the rightmost sink basin and turn on the water, then turn the water off and remove the now clean black rag.
Turn left and walk over to the toilet.
Put the clean black rag on the left side of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean black rag on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the white dresser.
Grab the dirty wash cloth off the top of the white dresser.
Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the dirty wash cloth in the right sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and walk to the toilet.
Put the clean cloth on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean wash cloth on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward to the door, then turn left and walk to the black cloth.
Pick up the black cloth from the dresser.
Turn left and walk forward to the two sinks.
Put the cloth in the sink on the right, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn left and walk forward to the toilet.
Put the cloth on the top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned cloth on the top of a toilet.
